import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import React from 'react'
import App from './App'

const persons = [
    {
      id: 1,
      name: 'Arto Hellas',
      number: '040 6571881',
    },
  ]
  
  ReactDOM.render(
    <App persons={persons} />,
    document.getElementById('root')
  )
